This report is based on available data and expert opinions up to October 2023. The dynamic nature of global markets and geopolitical events means that gas prices can be influenced by new developments not covered in this analysis. Additionally, while the report draws on multiple sources, it may not capture all perspectives or emerging trends in the energy sector.